      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly starter vehicle? This car is in poor condition and definitely shows its age, but it's ready for someone handy who isn't afraid of a little TLC! It's a great opportunity to get behind the wheel at a rock-bottom price while you restore it to its former glory. Grab a bargain and make this car your next weekend project!",
