    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior has minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. The interior is clean with some light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. All mechanical components are in working order, and the car has been serviced regularly.",
