    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor suspension work in the near future. It is a solid, honest vehicle for someone looking for reliable transportation at a reasonable price.",
      "price": 21000.0,
