    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom condition. This motorcar represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector, exhibiting flawless exterior surfaces and a pristine interior environment. Each component has been preserved to the highest standard, ensuring a mechanical and aesthetic profile that rivals its original delivery state. For those who demand uncompromised excellence, this offering stands as a testament to meticulous stewardship.",
